{"word":"G3816 - παῖς - paîs - paheece - Child","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παῖς</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">paîs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">paheece</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Child</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun / பெயர்ச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வேலைக்காரர், வேலைக்காரன், தாசன், ஊழியக்காரர் - ஆண்பால் பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"1. a child, boy or girl"},{"paragraph":"2. servant, slave"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Perhaps from <a href=\"#/G3817 - παίω - paíō - pah'-yo/3817\">G3817</a>; a <i>boy</i> (as often <i>beaten</i> with impunity), or (by analogy) a <i>girl</i>, and (generally) a <i>child</i>; specifically a <i>slave</i> or <i>servant</i> (especially a <i>minister</i> to a king; and by eminence to God): - child, maid (-en), (man) servant, son, young man.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1701/1701\">G1701</a>, <a href=\"#/G1702/1702\">G1702</a>, <a href=\"#/G1703/1703\">G1703</a>, <a href=\"#/G3808/3808\">G3808</a>, <a href=\"#/G3812/3812\">G3812</a>, <a href=\"#/G3813/3813\">G3813</a>, <a href=\"#/G3814/3814\">G3814</a>, <a href=\"#/G3816/3816\">G3816</a>"}]}